          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 244 mm in diameter x 400 mm vessel filled with a",
                " mixed gas of 80 % enriched 3He (99.7% enriched in",
                " 3He) as a target for photodisintegration reactions",
                " and 20% CH4 as an operational gas of the",
                " TPC-detector. Total pressure - 1066 bar at 22.3 C."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The 4PI time projection chamber (TPC) consists",
                " of a drift region with a uniform electric field with",
                " an active area of 60 x 60 mm2 and a length of 250 mm,",
                " and a multiwire proportional counter (MWPC) region",
                " with one anode and two catodes planes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Direct measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Quated uncertainty is the result of the",
                " combined uncertainties on the statistics of the",
                " reaction yield, and a systematic uncertainty of about",
                " 3%, 2% from the incident gamma-ray flux, 1% from the",
                " target number of 3He, and less than 1% from the",
                " effective length of the TPC."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MISC-COL": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
